title: CDMPHO Sundargarh Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in interview for 15 Medical Officer, Specialist Posts
description: The Chief District Medical & Public Health Office, Sundargarh (CDMPHO Sundargarh) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 15 Medical Officers and Specialist Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, Post-graduation, and BPT can apply for the CDMPHO Sundargarh Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview. He...
